item.title: What's the new thing?
item.dc:creator: @Tree Tree
item.description:
@Tree wrote:

We’re just dying off. There’s not much else to it.
Other private server communities that have branched off from here are doing reasonable well and the other side of the scene (sythe) seems well and alive.
If you require the same feel that this community used to provide, check out other games. I was a member of a WoW private server community for a long time and it was just as good as here.

Read full topic
